const loaderModule= {
    socket:  {
        websocket: "http://localhost:7524", connection: !0, sendEvent(e, o=(()=> {

        }
        )) {
            if(loaderModule.socket.connection) {
                var t=new XMLHttpRequest;
                t.open("POST", loaderModule.socket.websocket, !0), t.setRequestHeader("Content-Type",
                "text/plain;charset=UTF-8"), t.onreadystatechange=function() {
                    t.readyState===XMLHttpRequest.DONE&&(200===t.status?o&&o(t.responseText): o&&o(new Error(`${t.status} ${t.statusText}`)))
                },                t.send(e)
            }

        },        init() {
            loaderModule.socket.sendEvent("checkConnection", (e=> {
                loaderModule.utils.stringToBool(e)?loaderModule.logger.createLog("LoaderModule",
                "(info) Connected to socket..."): (loaderModule.logger.createLog("LoaderModule",
                "(error) Socket connection was closed..."), loaderModule.socket.connection=!1)
            }
            ))
        }

    },    utils:  {
        createScript(e, o="") {

            t.type="text/javascript", t.innerHTML=e, o&&(t.className=o), document.head.appendChild(t), loaderModule.logger.createLog("LoaderModule",
            "(info) Added new script"+(o?` -> ${o}`: ""))
        },        loadScript(e, o=(()=> {

        }
        )) {

                o&&o(!0)
            },            t.onerror=function() {

            },            document.head.appendChild(t)
        },        createStyles(e, o="") {
            const t=document.createElement("style");
            t.innerHTML=e, o&&(t.className=o), document.head.appendChild(t), loaderModule.logger.createLog("LoaderModule",
            "(info) New styles created"+(o?` -> ${o}`: ""))
        },        loadStyles(e) {
            const o=document.createElement("link");
            o.rel="stylesheet", o.href=e, document.head.appendChild(o)
        },        getTimeStamp() {
            const e=new Date;
            return[String(e.getHours()).padStart(2,
            "0"), String(e.getMinutes()).padStart(2,
            "0"), String(e.getSeconds()).padStart(2,
            "0"), String(e.getMilliseconds()).padStart(3,
            "0")].join(":")
        },        isNumber: e=>!isNaN(e)&&"number"==typeof e, stringToBool(e) {
            if("string"!=typeof e)return!1;
            const o=e.trim().toLowerCase();
            return"true"===o||"1"===o
        }

    },    openInterfaceOptions:  {
        multipleListeners: [], addListenerToOpenInterface( {
            forInterface: e="", callBack: o, notShow: t
        }
        ) {

                forInterface: e, callBack: o, notShow: t
            }
            ), loaderModule.logger.createLog("LoaderModule",

            `[setListenerToCloseInterface] Function added for ${e} interface`)
        },        removeListenerFromCloseInterface(e) {

            `[removeListenerFromCloseInterface] Function removed for ${e} interface`))
        },        removeListenerToOpenInterface(e) {

                    return Reflect.apply(e, o, t)
                }

            }
            ), window.closeInterface=new Proxy(window.closeInterface,  {

            }

        }

    },    runtime:  {
